name: Endless Snake
description:
This game is a version of the game Snake, except for the fact that you keep growing no matter what. 

Your goal is to eat at least 25 dots, and you have to fill up the entire screen. (outside of boundaries does not count.)

Anyone who can complete my challenge, I will put up a screenshot and their username in the screenshots for this game.

Move with arrow keys

It was made for the TI-84 Plus Silver Edition Calculator. It is compatible with other calculators in the TI family.

This program is compatible with:

TI-Nspire handhelds

TI-84 Plus Silver Edition

TI-84 Plus C Silver Edition

TI-84 Plus CE and TI-84 Plus CE-T

TI-84 Plus CE-T Python Edition and TI-84 Plus CE Python

TI-73

TI-83

TI-83 Plus

TI-89

TI-89 Titanium

TI-92

Voyage 200
